    "Multi-turn Interaction Domain.",
    "LLMs frequently interact with users across multiple turns, yet assessments typically focus on individual turns, overlooking their interactive capabilities.",
    "Thus, the MINT dataset (Wang et al, 2023e) is designed to evaluate LLMs in tasks involving multi-turn interactions, employing tools or utilizing natural language feedback.",
